            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-df98fb05b0686aa9-ef34de twpub-df98fb05b0686aa9-b916c4 twpub-df98fb05b0686aa9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c8\">*** END OF THE PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK THE LIFE AND ADVENTURES OF ROBINSON CRUSOE ***</div></div>"
